net.frozencode.jniolib.misc

Class TimeoutQueue<E>

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.frozencode.jniolib.misc.TimeoutQueue<E>
  • Type Parameters:
    E - the type of object stored by the queue.

    public class TimeoutQueue<E>
extends java.lang.Object
    The TimeoutQueue class implements a doubly-linked queue with all methods running in O(1) time. Elements are retrieved based upon how long they have been in the queue. This class is NOT Thread-Safe.
    Author:
    James Smith

    • Nested Class Summary

      Nested Classes 
      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      static class  TimeoutQueue.TimeoutQueueNode<E>
      The TimeoutQueueNode class stores data for a single element of a TimeoutQueue and provides a method move its element to the back of the TimeoutQueue in O(1) time.
